name: Genuine Large 200G 3M Perfect It Cleaner Clay Bar
description: This a medium grade detailing clay. Designed for the professional or enthusiast this is a large 200g bar. It is safe for use on painted surfaces and glass and has a medium amount of cut. It is a smooth textured clay and as such is safe to be used regularly and is ideal for removing all kinds of bonded contamination from paint. The main causes of contamination are industrial fallout, brake dust, bug splats, overspray and tree sap. So in summary if you need a clay bar with a little more cut than the dedicated enthusiast clays, but not so heavy it can cause marring on paint then this makes for an excellent choice of detailing clay.
